HomeConstants.particleLogin_prompt: Create a login page with particle animation background. Particles interact with mouse movements. Include floating card, gradient text, subtle hover animations, and smooth form validation/success effects.
HomeConstants.fireworks_prompt: Use Canvas to build a full-screen fireworks particle generator supporting various colors, shapes, and explosion modes. Include auto-play and mouse-triggered effects with starry background and gradient transitions. Smooth particle animation with full lifecycle effects.
HomeConstants.timeline_prompt: Build a vertical interactive timeline component with content cards, image display, and progress indicators. Add scroll-triggered animation, expandable details, and smooth navigation.
HomeConstants.imageFilter_prompt: Create a real-time image filter application supporting multiple filters, parameter adjustments, and before/after comparison. Includes drag-and-drop upload, download saving, and filter combinations. Modern UI for image preview.
HomeConstants.particleAvatar_prompt: Create a particle-based avatar generator: after uploading an image, convert the avatar into dynamic particles that follow the cursor, disperse/aggregate, and gently drift. Implemented with Canvas for a clean and visually striking page.
HomeConstants.glassDashboard_prompt: Build a full-screen glassmorphic dashboard with frosted glass cards, gradient background, statistic modules, and chart placeholders. Maintain consistent corner radius, shadows, and transparency for a modern, high-quality glass UI.
HomeConstants.glassCard_prompt: Create a set of glassmorphic cards with 3D tilt effects. The cards slightly rotate based on mouse movement with translucent textures, soft shadows, and highlights. When idle, the cards float subtly (up-down or slight rotation). Clean layout, strong sense of space, smooth animation.
HomeConstants.kanban_prompt: Use react-beautiful-dnd to build a draggable Kanban board with tasks that can be added or removed using local state. Consistent spacing, column width, and hover effects for a polished UI.
